minaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/02\/prophet-many-nights-hungry\/","url_meta":{"origin":25983,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hunger: The Prophet spent many nights hungry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 2, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would spend several nights in a row with an empty stomach, and his family would not find anything for dinner. Most of their bread was made from barley. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2360 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25976,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/02\/26\/prophet-ate-fill-with-guests\/","url_meta":{"origin":25983,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet only ate his fill with guests","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 26, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, never combined a dish of his with meat and bread for lunch, nor for dinner, unless he was eating with a gathering of people. Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 13859 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26036,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/03\/12\/prophet-full-stomach-khubz\/","url_meta":{"origin":25983,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Food: The Prophet never filled his stomach with bread","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 12, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, left this world while he had never ate to his fill of barley bread. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5098 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062e\u064e\u0631\u064e\u062c\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5441,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/20\/no-one-smile-more-muhammad\/","url_meta":{"origin":25983,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Smiling: No one smiled more than the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn al-Harith reported: I have not seen anyone smile more often than the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304\u00a03641 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u062b\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u